headline: Why PulteGroup (PHM) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of homebuilding company PulteGroup (NYSE:PHM) jumped 3.5% in the morning session after Citizens initiated coverage on the stock with a Market Outperform rating and set a price target of $145.00.

headline: Wall Street Bulls Look Optimistic About PulteGroup (PHM): Should You Buy?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for PulteGroup (PHM) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?
